was that the McCallisters?

464
00:38:28.723 --> 00:38:31.182
Yeah.
Call me in Paris.

465
00:38:31.267 --> 00:38:33.893
You're right.
They're gone.

466
00:38:37.231 --> 00:38:40.108
I knew they were.
Silver tuna tonight.

467
