by the American Dental Association?

470
00:38:55.374 --> 00:38:58.168
Well. I don't know.

471
00:38:58.252 --> 00:39:02.088
- It doesn't say. hon.
- Can you please find out?

472
00:39:05.051 --> 00:39:07.052
- Herb!
- Yeah?

473
00:39:07.136 --> 00:39:10.972
I've got a question here
about a toothbrush.

474
00:39:16.479 --> 00:39:20.815
Do you know. is this toothbrush
approved by the American
Dental Association?

475
00:39:20.900 --> 00:39:22.817
I don't know.

476
00:39:43.631 --> 00:39:48.051
- Just tell him that—
- Oh. hon. you pay for that here.

477
00:39:48.135 --> 00:39:50.053
Why don't you just
tell him it's approved?

478
00:39:50.137 --> 00:39:53.515
[ Woman ]
