00:40:08.114 --> 00:40:09.864
Shoplifter!

483
00:40:13.077 --> 00:40:14.953
Hey! Hey. kid!

484
00:40:15.037 --> 00:40:17.664
Come back here!

485
00:40:17.748 --> 00:40:20.500
[ Woman ]
Watch it!

486
00:40:21.836 --> 00:40:23.670
Come back here!

487
00:40:23.754 --> 00:40:27.674
Stop it. will ya!
Come here!

488
00:40:30.261 --> 00:40:37.475
Whoa! Whoa!

489
00:40:39.770 --> 00:40:42.480
Yeehaw!

490
00:41:06.255 --> 00:41:08.256
I'm a criminal.

491
00:41:35.409 --> 00:41:38.161
What's so funny?

492
00:41:38.245 --> 00:41:40.914
What's so funny?
What are you laughin' at?

493
00:41:43.542 --> 00:41:45.502
You did it again. didn't you?

494
00:41:45.586 --> 00:41:48.296
You left the water runnin'. didn't you?

495
00:41:48.380 --> 00:41:51.591
What's wrong with you?
I told you not to do it.

496
00:41:51.675 --> 00:41:53.593
Harry. it's our calling card.

497
00:41:53.677 --> 00:41:56.429
- Calling card.
- All the great ones leave their mark.

498
00:41:56.514 --> 00:41:58.431
We're the "Wet Bandits."

499
00:41:58.516 --> 00:42:01.392
You're sick. you know that?
You're really sick.

500
00:42:01.477 --> 00:42:03.394
- I'm not sick.
- Yes. you are.

501
00:42:03.479 --> 00:42:05.438
I'm not sick!
That's a sick thing to do!

502
00:42:12.154 --> 00:42:16.199
- We don't need that heat.
- Don't tell me what to do.
I can do it if I want to.

503
00:42:16.283 --> 00:42:19.077
- You're sick.
- I'm not sick.

504
00:42:19.161 --> 00:42:22.288
Hey. watch out!

505
00:42:28.796 --> 00:42:32.382
Hey. Hey!
You gotta watch out
for traffic. son. you know?

506
00:42:32.466 --> 00:42:34.884
- Sorry.
- Damn.

507
00:42:34.969 --> 00:42:37.262
Santy don't visit the funeral homes.
little buddy.

508
00:42:37.346 --> 00:42:39.556
[ Harry ]
Okay. okay.

509
00:42:39.640 --> 00:42:42.976
Merry Christmas.

510
00:42:52.361 --> 00:42:55.738
- What's the matter?
- I don't like the way that kid looked at me.

511
00:42:55.823 --> 00:42:57.740
- Did you see that?
- You ever seen him before?

512
00:42:57.825 --> 00:43:00.577
I saw a hundred kids this week.

513
00:43:00.661 --> 00:43:03.162
Let's see what house he goes into.

514
00:43:34.778 --> 00:43:37.071
[ Marv ]
Why is he goin' faster?

515
00:43:37.156 --> 00:43:41.576
I told you something's wrong.
I knew he looked at me weird.
Why would he run?

516
00:44:16.945 --> 00:44:21.032
[ Marv ] Maybe he went in the church.
- I'm not goin' in there.

517
00:44:21.116 --> 00:44:23.910
- Me neither.
- Ah. let's get out of here.

518
00:44:42.554 --> 00:44:45.723
When those guys come back.
I'll be ready.

