785
01:06:40.329 --> 01:06:43.415
♪ In sin and error pining ♪

786
01:06:43.499 --> 01:06:45.750
♪ Till he appeared ♪

787
01:06:45.835 --> 01:06:50.672
♪ And the soul felt his worth ♪

788
01:06:50.756 --> 01:06:53.925
